snippet: THE MARYLAND ELECTION.--Our telegraphic advices gives us a pretty fair indication of the result of the Congressional election in five of the six districts of Maryland. First District.--BOWIE, the regular Whig candidate is believed to be elected....
lead_paragraph: THE MARYLAND ELECTION.--Our telegraphic advices gives us a pretty fair indication of the result of the Congressional election in five of the six districts of Maryland. First District.--BOWIE, the regular Whig candidate is believed to be elected.
